        "subject": "LU-11771 ldlm: fix timeout in tgt_handle_re/connect message",
        "message": "LU-11771 ldlm: fix timeout in tgt_handle_re/connect message\n\nFunctions target_handle_connect/reconnect show incorrect\ntimeout to the end of recovery:\nfs1-OST0000: Recovery already passed deadline 71578:57.\nIf you do not want to wait more, please abort the recovery by force.\n...\nfs1-OST0000: Denying connection for new client ...\n(1 recovered, 11 in progress, and 1 evicted) to recover in 71578:57\n\nIt is incorrect to compare the result of ktime_get_seconds and\njiffies converted to seconds.\n\nCray-bug-id: LUS-6324\nChange-Id: If1e2bce74db9522d2e700b4ed848f7be7dc71e68\nSigned-off-by: Sergey Cheremencev <c17829@cray.com>\nReviewed-on: https://es-gerrit.dev.cray.com/153965\nReviewed-by: Andrew Perepechko <c17827@cray.com>\nReviewed-by: Andriy Skulysh <c17819@cray.com>\nTested-by: Elena Gryaznova <c17455@cray.com>\n"
